{
  "id": "adv_love_2311_06_01",
  "title": "Episode 6 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――高校三年生　春休み",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Third year of high school‚\nspring break",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "休憩を提案する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh006.m4a",
              "text": "俺も終わったよ\nお茶を淹れるから一休みしよう",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm done too.\nI'll make some tea‚\nso let's take a break.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 86.1666776937,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "外出を提案する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh007.m4a",
              "text": "俺も終わったよ\n息抜きに、どこか出かけないか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm done too.\nWant to go out\nsomewhere for a change of pace?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 90.1369497261,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "応援する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "おめでとう。渚は本当に凄いな\n俺も渚の本が読めるのは嬉しい\n応援してるよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Congratulations. You're really\namazing‚ Nagisa. I'm happy to\nbe able to read your book.\nI'm backing you up.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 170.6342119498,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 179.9353686931
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs014.m4a",
              "text": "うん……ありがとう\n……ね。手、握っていい？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Yeah… thank you.\n…Hey. Can I hold your hand?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 179.9353686931,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "え？　いいけど……\n渚、なんで……そんな顔……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Huh? Sure‚ but… Nagisa‚\nwhy… are you making that face…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 188.7687020264,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs015.m4a",
              "text": "{user}くん……\nどこかに行っちゃったりしないよね？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "{user}-kun… You're\nnot going anywhere‚ are you?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 195.5109922451,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "渚……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Nagisa…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 200.3443255784,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "（渚がどんどん離れていく気がしてたけど\nそう思ってたのは俺だけじゃなかった\n渚だって……不安なんだ）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（I felt like Nagisa was going\nfar away from me‚ but I wasn't\nthe only one who felt that way.\nNagisa was… insecure‚ too.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 202.2508777899,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "もちろんだ\n俺は……ずっと渚のそばにいるから",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Of course.\nI'll… always be by your side‚ Nagisa.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 211.9887236876,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs016.m4a",
              "text": "……うん、ありがとう",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Yeah‚ thank you.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 217.4380669238,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "（このままじゃ……いけない\nそんな気がした）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（I had a feeling that…\nI shouldn't let this go on.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 220.0047315559,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "勉強を促す",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "いいことだとは思うけど\n今は勉強に専念するべきじゃないか？\n出版社の人も分かってくれるさ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It's a good thing‚ but I think\nyou should focus on study now?\nProbably the publishing house\nwill understand too.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 225.7342072449,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 232.9208737972
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs017.m4a",
              "text": "……そう……かな\nでも……挑戦してみたい気持ちもあって……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Is that so…? But… I also\nwant to take on this challenge…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 232.9208737972,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "……俺、なんだか渚がどんどん\n遠くへ行っちゃうように感じるよ\nこのままじゃ、俺達……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I feel like you're drifting further\nand further away‚ Nagisa.\nIf this continues‚ we…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 239.320868711,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs018.m4a",
              "text": "なんで、なんでそんなこと言うの……？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Why‚ why are you saying that…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 247.8929319027,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs019.m4a",
              "text": "私、{user}くんに\n背中を押してもらえたから頑張れたんだよ？\nなのに、なのに……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I was able to make it this far‚\nsince you encouraged me.\nBut‚ but…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 251.7929319027,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 258.7476712826
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh021.m4a",
              "text": "……ごめん。でも、一緒にいる時間が\nだんだんなくなっていくのが辛くて……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I'm sorry. But‚ it makes me hurt\nspending less and less time\ntogether…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 259.4595985694,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 264.5966673496
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs020.m4a",
              "text": "そんなの……私だって同じだよっ！\nあ……ごめん、いきなり大声出して",
              "translations": {
                "en": "That's… how I feel‚ too!\nAh… sorry‚ I suddenly yelled.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 264.5966673496,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh022.m4a",
              "text": "い、いや、大丈夫\n俺も言い方が悪かったよ……ごめん",
              "translations": {
                "en": "N-no‚ it's okay.\nthe way I said was bad… I'm sorry.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 274.7300006829,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh023.m4a",
              "text": "（その後、俺は悪化してしまった関係を\nなんとかしようと同じ大学を目指さないか\nと提案した）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（After that‚ I suggested to aim\nfor the same university together\nto fix our relationship‚）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 281.3849419239,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh024.m4a",
              "text": "（賛成してはもらえたものの、渚は執筆に\n追われ、俺は渚との関係に悩み、二人とも\n勉強に身が入らないまま時は流れて――）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（She agreed‚ but she was busy with\nher writing‚ and I was troubled by our\nrelationship. Time passed‚ yet we\ncouldn’t focus on our studies――）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 288.612916148,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_park-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.5999999642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "は～、あとちょっとで春休みも終わりか～\n私達、もう三年生なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ spring break is almost over.\nWe're third years already.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4333332975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "受験勉強、頑張らないとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to work hard on studying\nfor the entrance exams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5999999642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.6999995827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "う……ヤなこと思い出させないでよ、も～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… don't remind me of those\nunpleasant things‚ no~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6999995827,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.333369100001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 18.0924487709
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.7333329518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　誰からだろ……はい、もしもし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Who is this…? Hello?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2333358406,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1696.664159400001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 26.1666682839
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1666682839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_06_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　き、金賞ですか！？\nありがとうございます！\n詳しくはまた後日……はい、はい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? G-gold prize!?\nThank you!\nmore detail later… Yes‚ yes…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1666682839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11896.665303699998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
