      "text": "うん！　前に応募した小説が金賞をとったの\n大賞はとれなかったけど、それでもデビュー\n出来るって……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! The novel I submitted\nbefore won the gold prize.\nI didn't get the grand prize‚\nbut they said I can debut…!",
        "id": ""
